Dialogs.Dialog: Hah, everyone put their hands together and say "bon appetit" like they're in kindergarten. Every day...
Eh？ I've been a Kobayakawa since birth, so what？
What are you blabbering on about, you look like an idiot.
(Is this an elementary school classroom？ I see, I'm in elementary school.)
Did you see last week's episode of Volvavin？
Huh？ Volvavin is... that robot anime？
That's it, I guess girls don't watch it？
It's not about whether you are a girl or a boy.
You are too much of a kid to watch robot anime at 4th grade.
And what？ The idea of girls and boys is fake to begin with. Do you know what "jendaa" means？ "Jendaa".
Eh？ It's... that... It doesn't matter if I explain it anyway, because you won't understand. It's not worth explaining.
(It's kind of like a Showa era school lunch...)
Why are you acting so suspicious？ It's not uncommon for school lunches to be served at school now.
You're right, I eat them every day...
I didn't leave them... I just didn't eat them.
Not at all. Rinko's is a gourmet, not a picky eater. She is a gourmet who does not eat bad food.
You eat everything, or you just have a poor sense of taste.
Yes！ ...I know, if it bothers you so much, I'll give you some.
Don't be afraid to say yes. Here, sneak a peek...
Hey, Kobayakawa-san！ Are you leaving your school lunch again！？
And trying to get someone else to eat it！
Come on, I'll keep you company. Just take your time and eat by yourself, okay？
(Heh, you look cute for your age...)
What's with the sudden uptight attitude！
(A dream, huh... I wonder if you were like that since elementary school, ▲小早川＊▲.)
Mysterious secret society, Deux Kisses, appears in New Towa Town. With the pulse of misfortune, is everyone in town unlucky！？
Rinko, however, is as follows♪ Hapikamurinko second season, good luck today, Hapikamurinko～♪
What？ Hapikamurinko？ That's the one I saw before...
Oh, amazing！ It really is Hapikamurinko！
Of course！ I'll help you all to have good luck♪
Yeah... Let me explain, okay？ Rinko changed her mind after being baptized by Happi Breath at the end of the first season！ She is no longer the downer, stick-talking magical girl she used to be！
Who is a dark-rooted, radish actor！
Tsk！ The AD there is... No, it's nothing. Right, Dad？
That's right！ Rinko！ Your father is impressed！
Hi, Dad. Thank you very much for your help the other day... You gave me a terrible time.
Was it really？ Never mind, boy in front of the TV！
Well, that's okay... But more importantly, I'm glad. It was a low-budget show, but they aired the second season.
Well, I guess？ This is another of Rinko's talents, hehe. The pay was a bit higher, too...
I know！ Let me introduce you to Rinko's happy friend, Manaka-chan♪
Hey there！ Rakiraki Manapyon, here I come～♪
You should choose the job you want to do, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Hey, can I get out soon？
What exactly is your role ▲姉ヶ崎＊▲？
I am Amazone-ne, Secretary of the mysterious secret society Deux Kisses！ I'll shoot your happiness down！
...I'll be mad if you move, okay？
W-Wow！ It's Dixie's Amazone-ne！ Don't let her suck your happiness away！
It's because it was too sudden！
You are disqualified as an extra.
Well, we can't afford to be extravagant. Okay, let's get back on track！
Hey, what kind of training do you have at your office to make your cell phone ring during a performance？
I-It's because... Oh, it's the producer！
Hello... Yes... Um, I'm in the middle of a production. What！？
Rounding up the second term, the third term "Hapikamu Three"！？ Wait, wait, what do you mean "three"？ What do you mean, you're coming here？
Manaka-chan, Nene-chan, are we doing it？
Hey, what do you mean with three！？
Oh, sorry. The sponsors wanted to sell more toys, so we tripled the main characters, tripled the merchandise, and had a lot of fun (laughs).
Three characters... Rinko's the center, right？ And, what about my pay！？
I would decide the center by election, hapikamu general election. If there is a sub-character that becomes popular, it will be a sub-committee.
What！？ I'm not kidding！ Rinko's the immovable center！ And my pay！
Oops～？ I'm sensing danger, well, I'm off to Girappon for MTG after this... See ya！
Rinko, this is just a boundary！ Don't lose！
Ugh... even though it's a crown jewel of the show...
I have to campaign... First, I have to ask Papa to help me build my local base...
To one in front to the TV～？ If you could, please vote for your onee-san, fufufu▼
Hmm, is there also a Daruma here？
Idiot！ Idiot！ Get out of here！ Hapikamurinko～♪
...Well, it was a dream after all.
Will there really be a third phase？
This is a government inspection. If you confront us, we will cut you down without mercy！
Rinko Kobayakawa, Captain of the Shinsengumi First Squadron. Here I come！
Huh？ What's with the outfit！ And, why are you holding a toy sword, ▲小早川＊▲...？
Why are you spacing off for？ Are those two bars on your waist just for decoration！？
You can't strike with just the two of you！ We're gonna get you back！
I had no idea that so many recalcitrant Ronin were lurking in Ikedaya. But we will hold out until the bureau chiefs arrive！
Kobayakawa-sensei！ If we don't do something, we'll get retaliated against. We should retreat at once.
...Then you alone must flee. I will cut through their enclosure.
Nonsense！ Sensei and I are partners, we go everywhere together.
But... if we keep this up, we'll both be...
We'll be together when we die. That's what we swore！ I'm not leaving you！
I will not let you die here！ Together, we will cut through this enclosure！
Sensei！ The wound is shallow, be careful！
...Sorry, I don't think I can keep my promise. So... just run away... and...
Don't die！ I won't allow you to die alone like this, ▲小早川＊▲！
Hehe, your face is getting getting far away...
This blood... is kind of dry, isn't it？ And this smell...
...What are you talking about？ It's just normal bloodstains, of course.
Bloodstains, huh... this is just tomato juice, isn't it？
I was looking for something to use as a bloodstain, but I couldn't find it. Then I found tomato juice on the table.
I'm not sure why it was there... Yuck, that smells like tomato juice...
What's wrong？ You look really pale.
Rinko, you know... I forgot that I hate tomatoes... Idiot.
I'm losing consciousness... I'll leave the rest to you. That's all.
Wait a minute！ If you want to lose consciousness, you'll have to break through this enclosure... Ha, hahahaha.
Um... you're not going to let me get away of this... situation, are you？
Please, wake up！！ There's no way I can defeat all of them by myself, ▲小早川＊▲！
Ah... a dream. That kind of outfit suits you, ▲小早川＊▲.
(Slide across the screen like you're slashing at the enemy with this sword！)
Slide the screen to cut the enemy
Huh... where am I... Ah, ▲小早川＊▲？
It is me... It's Princess Thumbelina. Don't you remember me, Swallow-san？
Swallow？ Huh... Am I a Swallow！？
Ah, I'm sorry... By the way, you've become small once more, ▲小早川＊▲.
(Shucks, did you get mad at me for saying you're tiny？)
Are you crying？ What's wrong... ▲小早川＊▲？
Actually, I am going to be married to a mole.
Mole-san is from the underground world, and when I get married, of course I will also go underground where there is no sun... ugh...
(You're so different from usual, neat and fragile... You are so cute, ▲小早川＊▲.)
All right, I get it！ I'll take care of it！
What's the big deal？ If there is money, there is love, too.
Hehehe. I love you, Thumbelina～I love you.
Our marriage is officially approved by Rat Obaa-san, you know？ All that's left is your reply～.
Thumbelina doesn't like it, you know. Don't force yourself on her.
Thumbelina is just anxious to be underground where she's never lived, she'll get used to that.
Don't get in my way. So you can make Thumbelina happy？ You got money？ Money～？
Well... I'm still in high school...
I can' t give you Thumbelina like that～, I can't give her to you～.
Do you believe in me, ▲小早川＊▲？
This is the kind of boyfriend you have, but do you still believe in me？
Even if I don't have money or status, I love her the most！ I can make you the happiest, ▲小早川＊▲！
That's just a bunch of young, beautiful talk！
Don't mind the young man's pretty words, because I'm still young！
Yes, I understand. Come with me to the Land of Flowers！
Yes！ I'll follow you wherever you go！
Are you okay？ Hold on to me so you don't fall off.
Actually, Rinko is pretty good at racing games and flight simulators.
Eh, you're the type that changes when you take the wheel！？
I should be careful when you get a car licence, ▲小早川＊▲.
(I didn't really feel it at first, but... I don't having a child...)
(A loving wife, adorable kids... it's the best！)
Yes, it was more dangerous at first.
Oh, but after the birth of my child, I suddenly became more reliable... or, more of an adult woman.
Now that you mention it, you're already an adult.
It's not sudden... You gave me so many treasures.
When I was in high school and you became my boyfriend...
I didn't think there was anything happier than that.
Yeah... Then again, I was surprised when we got married.
We had been together for so long before that, I thought, surely marriage wouldn't change anything.
...Conversations with you, and everyday life, they are all the same as they were before.
The only thing that was growing inside of me was the feeling that I loved you.
I felt a greater happiness then, but... it's different now.
It's not just "I love you" when it's just the two of us. It's more about something else...
Seeing this precious little girl makes me feel good about myself. It also... makes me happy.
A boyfriend, a husband, and a baby... you gave everything to me.
I owe my happiness to you. So, thank you.
That's the same for me, thank you...
Tears... I see, I was crying.
Good morning. I'm the head of the department, and I've been assigned as your trainer. Nice to meet you, my name is ▲苗字▲▲名前▲.
My name0s Rinko Kobayakawa, and I am a newcomer. I will do my best, so please give me your guidance.
Yeah, keep up the good work！
...Kobayakawa-kun is polite and pleasant. I have high hopes for you！
No, that's... Thank you very much.
Mm-hmm. Well, let's get one job done right away...
Is there anything you need help with？
Thank you very much. No problem so far.
I was listening to this while commuting to work... I think I forgot to stop it.
That's fine, but put it away while you're on duty.
It's okay. Well then, please continue.
Kobayakawa-kun. I asked you earlier to create a table. How's it coming？ Don't tell me you've already finished？
Um, no, I'm almost there... But it is going well.
Oh, um！ It's that... I was doing some research！ I was searching for something I didn't understand, and I came across this bulletin board...
Hmm... I see. Then it's... huh？ Fighting game strategy？
Oh... Isn't it just your imagination？
Don't you "hehe" me. Do you really think you can make a living with this kind of attitude from the very beginning of your career？ Good grief...
Shut up, you should have listened to me earlier. Who do you think you are, Chief-sama？
I don't feel motivated if I am told not to do this or that.
You say that, but you're on duty.
If you do any more, I will sue you for power harassment.
Director！ Please help me！ The chief, the chief is... to me...
You idiot！ You'll have to start over from the newcomer training！ Instead, Kobayakawa-kun, you are now the chief.
Yes, I respectfully accept your offer.
Huh... I'm glad that was a dream. It was terrible...
But the way you looked on a suit was great, ▲小早川＊▲...
(Is this sound coming from the desk？)
(Let's take a look at the computer...)
Go, go, TOWANO！ Let's go, TOWANO！
(I'll ask Rinda out for the prom...)
Oops, I shouldn't have done that. I haven't introduced myself yet.
My name is... ▲名前▲！ I'm the quarterback of TOWANO CITY's prestigious Forever High School football team.
To be precise... Yeah, I'm an alternate who wants to be a quarterback. Or so they say.
Rinda, the cheerleader, is too good for me... but next time I'm going to ask Rinda to prom！
Ah, no！ It's nothing！ Forget it！
Hey, will you go with me to cheer practice？ If you do well, I'll do you anything you want.
It's fine, come on！ Repeat after me！
Yeah！ Ｆ・Ｏ・Ｒ・Ｅ・Ｖ・Ｅ・Ｒ ＦＯＲＥＶＥＲ！
...Then, what do you want me to do？
Don't you want to ask for anything？
You haven't decided who you're going to prom with yet, have you？ Hey, hey, go with me
Ri-Rinda's going to prom with... me！ You stay out of this！
Hehehe... What are you talking about, dude？
Wait, there's no way I can compete with the players！
Rinda... go to prom with me！
...Yeah... sounds good. Hehe, that was cool...
Don't underestimate the Forever High School kicker！
Um... it was Rinda, or was it Rinko...
What are you doing spacing out！
You think you can spare the time to not even look up the names of your opponents！
(I see, I'm going to be at a fighting tournament...)
That's not a small kick！ That was something amazing.
That was a lever front- loaded small kick.
(I guess I should fight back too...)
Hmm, are you coming or not？
(But wait... fighting back means... I can't touch my girlfriend！)
What's the matter, won't you come？
Tsk, you put your guard up.
(If this happens, I'm going to run until time runs out and we'll call it a tie！)
Kuh, you're good at running away.
Hah, haha... I think I can manage...
...You think so？ Thanks to my continued attacks, my gauge is full.
Once the gauge is full, prepare to take on a special move！
Here goes, a series of small kicks～！
(It felt kind of warm, soft, and comfortable...)
(You are sleeping so unprotected. Unbelievable, even though your boyfriend is on top of you, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(And, aren't you getting kind of big, ▲小早川＊▲？)
(Somehow, I feel I have more hair...)
Did you wake up？ Rinko is still going to sleep, good night...
(What on earth is going on here？)
(Okay, I'm going to get back at you for all the yelling and kicking I usually get...)
(Crap, she's going to wake up... I have to put her back to sleep...)
(To put her to sleep... I'll try rocking the hammock...)
Nya～ Nya nya～♪ Nya～ Nya nya～♪
(Oh no, you're totally awake. So much for this.)
Hehe, did you sleep well too？
I see, I see, you're so cute▼
(Wow, my body is pressed up against your chest...)
Nya！ Nya nya！ (Wait, you're hugging me too hard！)
(Ugh, ouch！ Ouch！ I'm not that cute！)
*Phew*... even though I'm used to it, it's still hot.
(How long has it been since we started living on a deserted island, ▲小早川＊▲...)
(Unlike me, who has yet to give up hope of rescue, you already gone bonkers, ▲小早川＊▲...)
Yeah, I brought fish and fruits！
Hey, what's up with that monkey？
This guy？ Rinko picked it up！ It'll come in handy！
Glub glub... it's yummy！ You also try！
You look so sleazy... Get away from ▲小早川＊▲！
I knew it, you are Rinko's！ Rinko is yours！
Yes, I believed in you, ▲小早川＊▲...
Yeah, Rinko, wherever you are, even if it's just the two of us on this island forever...
With you, only you, Rinko's partner, ▲主人公＊▲！
You look tastier than that hairy guy！
Hah, hah, hah... It was a dream...
I never thought my girlfriend was going to eat me...
I'd like to refrain from such expressions of affection...
(I'll swing as hard as the monkey！)
